               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17930220-4-cd17" type="crimeDate">18th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930220-4-off16 t17930220-4-cd17"></join>, ten pair of silk hose, value 15 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930220-4-victim92" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Clarke
